SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. MARC ROSENBERG from April 1 to 4, 2014, inclusive; (2) the Hon. HEATHER J. TULLOCH from April 28 to 30, 2014, inclusive.
